 \frac{2^{2n+1} n!(n+1)!}{(2n+2)!}=\frac{\frac{n!}{\sqrt{2\pi n}\left(\frac{n}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^n} \cdot\frac{(n+1)!}{\sqrt{2\pi (n+1)}\left(\frac{n+1}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^{n+1}}}{\frac{(2n+2)!}{\sqrt{2\pi (2n+2)}\left(\frac{2n+2}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^{2n+2}}}\cdot \frac{2^{2n+1}\sqrt{2\pi (2n+2)}\left(\frac{2n+2}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^{2n+2}}{\sqrt{2\pi n}\left(\frac{n}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^n\cdot\sqrt{2\pi (n+1)}\left(\frac{n+1}{\mathrm{e}}\right)^{n+1}}. 
